  "title": "ISic003059. I.Sicily inscription 003059",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/VDAQH5D2\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/VDAQH5D2</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"aba\">fragment (physical) a</span>  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"diva--interpretive\">  <a id=\"aa-l1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δεκίμου Ἰουνίου\n                    ωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δεκίμου\">Δ(εκίμου)</span>  <span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰουνίου\">Ἰουνίου</span>  <br id=\"aa-l2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ωνος\">[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">.</span><span data-text=\"ωνος\">ωνος</span></span></span>  </span></div>  <span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abb\">fragment (physical) b</span>  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divb--interpretive\">  <a id=\"ab-l1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>ΓΑΚ </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/VDAQH5D2\">https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/VDAQH5D2</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"aba\">fragment (physical) a</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"diva--diplomatic\"><a id=\"aa-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δεκίμου Ἰουνίου\n                    ωνος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δεκίμου\">Δ</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Ἰουνίου\">ΙΟΥΝΙΟΥ</span><br id=\"aa-l2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ωνος\">[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">·</span><span data-text=\"ωνος\">ΩΝΟΣ</span></span></span></span></div><span class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"abb\">fragment (physical) b</span><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"divb--diplomatic\"><a id=\"ab-l1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>ΓΑΚ</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of I.Lipara</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2> translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\">  </p><p>  </p></div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Unclear whether the group of letters in the second fragment from the lower part of the stele is a monogram containing further letters or not.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 41.0814 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796</a></li><li> Bernabò Brea and Cavalier 1991 182 tomba 2179 inv.15382 fig.335 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002157\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002157</a></li><li>   Bernabó-Brea  Cavalier  Campagna  2003 677 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000541\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000541</a></li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.  </div>",
